{"tid":583511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵車長暈倒駕駛室 滿面鮮血被扶出月台","createTime":"2018-03-07T05:08:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T06:35:33.000Z","uid":39464,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"b4c55afbe6338ef8d2d8fa887b3509a90969c865","tid":583511,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T05:08:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180307/large/1520398799_579a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180307%2Flarge%2F1520398799_579a.jpg&h=3e84dcd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵列車車長，在駕駛室內暈倒跌穿頭。今晨10時許，荃灣綫一列車，在油麻地站上落客後，車門良久沒有關上。控制中心呼喚車長多次，一直沒有回覆，於是召月台職員前往查看，結果發現車長暈倒跌在駕駛室內，右眼角近耳朵位置受傷淌血。月台職員連忙通侠知控制中心，並將暈倒的車長扶到月台的凳上。<br />\n<br />\n該名資深車長姓廖約50歲，稍後轉醒過來，由救護車送到廣華醫院治理。至於涉事列車，須返車廠檢查，車上乘客要落車轉乘下一班車。<br />\n據了解，港鐵列車是自動化行駛，列車到站車門會自動打開，車長確定上落客後即人手按掣關門。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180307/57914667\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180307%2F57914667&d=rBBbksJCFdB8J9VfulbnZ8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=9fdba7b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180307%2F57914667&h=20eb2726\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180307/57914667</a>"},{"pid":"0add5564f4d109de4cd31f6f3049ad785e3eab74","tid":583511,"uid":2333,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T05:11:06.000Z","msg":"釣魚中左落control panel"},{"pid":"b8f85629dd04279cb7b5a430002176cf0dec887c","tid":583511,"uid":27485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T05:12:58.000Z","msg":"中槍咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8379aa27eb92960d7951bb2e4130fbe8d8a1a38b","tid":583511,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci